{"tid":419647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張雲正與「80後」新聞主任結婚　半島酒店宴請11席 ","createTime":"2017-09-30T16:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T10:15:00.000Z","uid":139114,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a25115d8e8e1cfebfffa159db4ef306be95f839d","tid":419647,"uid":139114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"年尾係結婚旺季，Emily聽聞，現年55歲嘅前公務員事務局長張雲正，將會同「80後」新聞主任呂卓穎（Florence）拉埋天窗，下個月中喺半島酒店擺酒同證婚，正式脫離「鑽石王老五」行列。據Emily所知，有政府中人近日已經收到請帖。<br />\nEmily今日就send咗短訊恭喜張雲正，佢多謝Emily祝福之餘，仲話婚禮係私人性質，筵開11席，主要邀請親朋戚友出席，只有個別政府舊同事獲邀，因為雙方都想盡量保持低調，希望大家理解。<br />\n<br />\n政務官出身嘅張雲正，加入問責團隊之前出任海關關長，據聞同當時喺海關做新聞主任嘅Florence邂逅。舊年3月，一幅影到佢哋便服拖篋現身機場嘅相喺公務員圈子瘋傳，令二人戀情曝光。今年7月，上屆問責團隊搞咗個飯局請前特首梁振英食飯，張雲正都有帶埋女友出席。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170929/s00001/1506691216127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170929%2Fs00001%2F1506691216127&d=wP3koozxvDs1WiWs1vL7wv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=aa471fa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170929%2Fs00001%2F1506691216127&h=fa013131\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170929/s00001/1506691216127</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dhxq0yui\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdhxq0yui&h=0e087d66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43481aa1ac1d588c7730234f19c30de5440b20b6","tid":419647,"uid":45772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"0dfcbb6faab4e1c28ee9c3ce6a59242a0d2587a2","tid":419647,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T20:39:54.000Z","msg":"55歲<br />\n酸鳩一定軟奶奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e60c9a1afa9b4bb35712bc2a77a3b91d1e62d4f","tid":419647,"uid":34013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,